=head1 INSTALLATION

These are the installation instructions for MIME::Detect.

The module releases are hosted on CPAN. The module
can be installed:

=over

=item latest release from CPAN

  cpan MIME::Detect

or

  cpanm MIME::Detect

=item directly, as the latest development files

 cpanm git://github.com/Corion/mime-detect.git

=item manually cloninig the repository:

 git clone git://github.com/Corion/mime-detect.git
 cd MIME_Detect
 perl Makefile.PL
 make
 make test
 make install

=back

